text:
Ah, no, I was just practicing my lines for the drama.
Sorry, if I startled you.

Oh, I see...!
Sorry for interrupting.
...I'll go buy some drinks from outside for a bit.

Wait! You don't have to do that!
Your consideration...

Your workplace is here,
so it's easier if I move.

But even so...
If Juri continues practicing like this without worrying...
